‘Harry Potter’ Actor Matthew Lewis Ties the Knot Matthew Lewis, or better known as Neville Longbottom for ‘Harry Potter’ fans, got married to Angela Jones in Italy over the weekend.  A post shared by  Matthew Lewis (@mattdavelewis) on May 28, 2018 at 9:46am PDT  He joked in a tweet about missing an Arctic Monkeys concert due to the wedding. Matthew Lewis, via Twitter. He wrote
“Not only did I miss @ArcticMonkeys in LA but they were performing in Italy at the same time we were there and my wife made me get married instead. Fuming,” TMZ reports that Lewis and Jones got engaged at the Eiffel Tower back in November 2016. **Reuters